'''Brad Freeman''' is the author of ''[[Scavenger Hunt]]'', an adventure for ''[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]'' from [[West End Games]]. Among other things, Freeman introduced the [[Squib/Legends|Squib]] and [[Ugor/Legends|Ugor]] species to the [[Canon|''Star Wars'' universe]].

